OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNHS 'riddled with racism'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagainst ethnic minority    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdoctors                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The NHS is "riddled with racism", the  
OL,6, chair of the British Medical           
OL,7, Association's council has told the BBC.
OL,9,FDr Chaand Nagpaul has spoken out in    
OL,10,Fresponse to a survey by the BMA, shared
OL,11,Fexclusively with BBC News.             
OL,13,FAt least 75% of ethnic minority doctors
OL,14,Fexperienced racism more than once in   
OL,15,Fthe last two years, while 17.4% said   
OL,16,Fthey regularly faced racism at work,   
OL,17,Fthe survey said.                       
OL,19,FNHS England said it takes a            
OL,20,F"zero-tolerance approach" to racism.   
